## Naming and tag validation

Before `terraform apply`, verify:

- Table name will be: `dyn-{env}-io-{{businessDomain}}-{{serviceDomain}}-{{tableName}}-{{versionProject}}`
- Tags match: `BUSINESS-DOMAIN={{businessDomain}}`, `SERVICE-DOMAIN={{serviceDomain}}`, `JOURNEY={{journey}}`, `FEATURE={{feature}}`, `OWNER={{owner}}`

If any tag differs from the value above, ask the developer before proceeding.

